  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 375°F (190°C).",
    "Marinate sausage with miso paste, ground cumin, smoked paprika, salt, and pepper for at least 2 hours.",
    "Sauté onions and garlic in olive oil until translucent.",
    "Add rice and sauté until it turns golden brown.",
    "Stir in marinated sausage, chicken broth, white wine (if using), heavy cream, and cumin. Bring to a simmer.",
    "Transfer mixture to an oven-safe dish. Bake for 20 minutes or until the sauce thickens and the rice is tender.",
    "Serve hot as a solo-dinner mediterranean-friendly Uruguayan dish."
